          The Alfa Laval UVNX 418 Decanter is a <a href="/three-phase-decanter/" class="text-[#1B3A5C] hover:text-[#E8A317]">three-phase decanter</a> centrifuge specially built for the three-phase separation of fish oil, olive oil, animal fat-rendering, etc.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#2D2D2D] mb-6">
          With a 25 HP Motor, the UVNX 418 decanter centrifuge has a bowl RPM of 4,000 and can process 70 GPM of Fish Oil and Meal Separation.
        </p>
        <img
          src="/images/alfa-laval-nx-418-decanter-centrifuge/Alfa-Laval-NX418-Decaner-C1D2-for-Hemp-Ethanol-Processing-600.webp"
